Job Description
Namal Education Foundation is constructing a university at Namal approximately 35 Km from Mianwali, Punjab. Following vacancies exist in the Project Department.
Civil Engineer:
Qualification: Degree in Civil Engineer from any University Recognized by HEC and should be registered with Pakistan Engineering Council.
Experience: 7 to 10 Years with reputable construction companies with minimum 7 years experience in the construction of Building, Roads and Infrastructure.
Should be a good team leader.
Should be well conversant with local and international codes of practices.
Shall be responsible for quality of work, control of budget and timely completion of work and allied activates.
Must have experience of plumbing, Electrical works and wood work.
Should be able to evaluate cost and prepare cost estimates/rate analysis.
Should be able to verify contractor's bills prepare and submit progress reports to the management.Apply Instructions for This Job
Application must be submitted along with C.V within 15 days of publication of this advertisement on the address given below. Only short listed candidate shall be contacted.
Project Director
Namal Education Foundation
75-D/1, Main Boulevard, Gulberg III, Liberty Roundabout, Lahore, Pakistan.
